==English==

===Noun===
'''bulb'''

# A solid rounded at one end and tapering on the other, possibly attached to a larger object at the tapered end
# A [[light bulb]]
# The bulb-shaped root portion of a plant such as a tulip, from which the rest of the plant may be regrown.

